data.description: Open floor concept with 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms raised ranch that is rarely available in the desirable Marynook community. Total renovation performed by experienced developer with a suburb feel in the city. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a welcoming living room that seamlessly connects to the dining area and kitchen, creating a fantastic open floor plan. Main level features stunning hardwood floors that add to the charm of the home. On the main level, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, ensuring ample space for your family needs. Lower level is a true gem with two fantastic recreational spaces, one of which includes a wet bar with quartz countertops and room for a beverage cooler. This space is perfect for entertaining friends and family. Additionally, the lower level hosts a spacious bedroom and another fully renovated bathroom, showcasing stunning tile work and high-quality finishes. Backyard is a delightful retreat, featuring a covered patio where you can relax and enjoy outdoor gatherings. Location is fantastic, with easy access to the expressway, stores, restaurants, and public transportation, making it convenient for daily commuting and leisure activities. This property is a true gem in the heart of Marynook, offering a combination of modern updates and classic charm. Welcome home!
